text: "2300 Jackson Street" is a 1989 song by The Jackson 5 featuring Janet Jackson and was taken from their 16th studio album 2300 Jackson Street. It went to number 76 in the United Kingdom and number 39 in the Netherlands. ==References== Category:1989 songs Category:The Jackson 5 songs Category:Janet Jackson songs Category:Michael Jackson songs
